All technical and gameplay data is stored locally on your device or collected by third-party services (AdMob, Firebase, Play Console).

We do not store any personal identifiers such as name, email, phone number, or payment info.

4. Children’s Privacy

The Game is not directed to children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children.

If you believe your child has provided personal data, please contact us, and we will take steps to remove it.

